  "about": "Ermes is one of Jolyne Cujoh's main allies. She is very prideful and loyal, preferring to act and think later.\n\n\n\nWhilst in Green Dolphin Street Prison, she acquires a Stand which she names 'Kiss' which allows her to place 'stickers' on items to duplicate them, but once the sticker is removed the two items smash together violently.",
